title: BOYZ II MEN - COLLIDE
description:
Here we have the latest release from BOYZ II MEN. It has been a long time since I have heard anything from this R&B/SOUL group that moved the crowd with their harmonies in the nineties.

After a long absence they have returned with a album called COLLIDE

Give it a listen and see if the fire is still there in BOYZ II MEN

Album Tracks:

1. Me, Myself and I
2. What Happens In Vegas
3. Diamond Eyes
4. Better Half
5. Underwater
6. Believe Us
7. Don't stop
8. Already Gone
9. A Long As I Am With You
10.So What
11.Collide
